ching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage"}}}